rows.label: tlk45300451_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Say, are those Blades I see
traveling with you? That
brings back memories...

rows.label: tlk45300451_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My old man's a Driver too,
you know. His Blade was
basically like a mother to me.

rows.label: tlk45300451_01_msg0003
rows.name:
She used to make me dumplings, play
with me, help with my education...

rows.label: tlk45300451_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I hope she's doing all right
these days. My old man, too...
